316
00:14:28,202 --> 00:14:29,202
Hi.

317
00:14:29,203 --> 00:14:30,231
(Regardless,)

318
00:14:30,232 --> 00:14:31,271
Hi.

319
00:14:31,272 --> 00:14:32,272
