320
00:14:32,273 --> 00:14:33,302
Hi.

321
00:14:34,012 --> 00:14:35,572
I'm the drama teacher.

322
00:14:36,672 --> 00:14:39,212
Please come when we hold a play.

323
00:14:39,582 --> 00:14:40,651
Thank you.

324
00:14:40,652 --> 00:14:44,082
