326
00:14:51,762 --> 00:14:54,162
I'm the drama teacher at Yongheung Elementary School.

327
00:14:59,032 --> 00:15:00,832
Isn't it interesting? It is, right?

328
00:15:01,202 --> 00:15:02,331
Exactly.

329
00:15:02,332 --> 00:15:04,072
- Would you like a bag?
- Yes, please.

330
00:15:11,982 --> 00:15:13,181
Are these camera films?

331
00:15:13,182 --> 00:15:14,482
(Camera film?)

332
00:15:14,652 --> 00:15:15,852
I'd like one.

333
00:15:16,312 --> 00:15:18,222
- That? Just take one.
- Yes.

334
00:15:18,852 --> 00:15:19,882
Thank you.

335
00:15:20,422 --> 00:15:21,451
Nice.

336
00:15:21,452 --> 00:15:23,792
