353
00:16:12,042 --> 00:16:13,902
The acting class has to gather.

354
00:16:14,112 --> 00:16:16,212
We have to practice during lunch.

355
00:16:16,442 --> 00:16:18,182
It was fun and nice.

356
00:16:18,312 --> 00:16:20,112
Once it ends,

357
00:16:20,582 --> 00:16:23,051
