364
00:16:35,192 --> 00:16:37,732
I'm going to give each of you...

365
00:16:37,802 --> 00:16:39,432
- Really?
- a camcorder.

366
00:16:39,532 --> 00:16:40,871
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

367
00:16:40,872 --> 00:16:42,002
It made me happy.

368
00:16:43,102 --> 00:16:45,302
(Recording his practice voluntarily)

369
00:16:45,942 --> 00:16:48,312
(Reading any lines smoothly)

370
00:16:48,472 --> 00:16:49,771
In 1, 2, 3.

371
00:16:49,772 --> 00:16:52,511
(Hyo Min is full of passion.)

372
00:16:52,512 --> 00:16:53,711
