376
00:17:01,752 --> 00:17:02,992
Four, six.

377
00:17:04,092 --> 00:17:06,792
(The goal of the 4th class is...)

378
00:17:07,562 --> 00:17:10,132
(reading the script.)

379
00:17:11,232 --> 00:17:13,702
(And the most important,)

