383
00:17:25,482 --> 00:17:27,281
- Hi, Ms. Kim.
- Hi.

384
00:17:27,282 --> 00:17:30,012
Hi.

385
00:17:30,412 --> 00:17:33,122
Thank you. Please hand in your notebook first.

386
00:17:33,322 --> 00:17:36,022
- I have to give it with both hands.
- Thank you.

387
00:17:37,822 --> 00:17:40,831
Guys, how was yesterday's outdoor class? Was it fun?

388
00:17:40,832 --> 00:17:42,091
- Yes!
- Yes!

389
00:17:42,092 --> 00:17:44,301
I had loads of fun too.

390
00:17:44,302 --> 00:17:47,431
But I prefer the gym.

391
00:17:47,432 --> 00:17:48,802
- What about you?
- I prefer the outside.

392
00:17:49,032 --> 00:17:50,032
Come on.

393
00:17:50,472 --> 00:17:51,501
- Come on.
- Fine.

394
00:17:51,502 --> 00:17:53,772
- Really?
- If she prefers it, then it's fine.

395
00:17:53,802 --> 00:17:56,772
- It's kind of...
- The gym isn't bad.

396
00:17:57,072 --> 00:17:59,781
All right, the gym is our space.

397
00:17:59,782 --> 00:18:02,311
Let's have another fun class, okay?

398
00:18:02,312 --> 00:18:03,351
- Okay.
- Okay.

399
00:18:03,352 --> 00:18:05,082
What are we going to do, Mr. Choi?

400
00:18:05,122 --> 00:18:06,122
We're going to warm-up.

401
00:18:06,123 --> 00:18:08,052
Remember what we did on our first day?

402
00:18:08,252 --> 00:18:10,521
Copy me along with the music, okay?

403
00:18:10,522 --> 00:18:11,522
Yes.

404
00:18:11,992 --> 00:18:13,591
(With fun music,)

405
00:18:13,592 --> 00:18:16,532
(it’s time to warm-up.)

406
00:18:16,962 --> 00:18:18,302
(Cheering)

407
00:18:19,702 --> 00:18:20,802
To the side.

408
00:18:21,472 --> 00:18:22,572
The other side.

409
00:18:24,572 --> 00:18:27,272
(With no pause)

410
00:18:27,672 --> 00:18:29,871
(You’re doing great, Potato Teacher.)

411
00:18:29,872 --> 00:18:30,981
Back to your spot. Squats.

412
00:18:30,982 --> 00:18:32,641
(Back to your spot. Squats.)

413
00:18:32,642 --> 00:18:33,681
One,

414
00:18:33,682 --> 00:18:34,852
- They're doing it.
- two,

415
00:18:35,352 --> 00:18:36,482
- They're doing it.
- three,

416
00:18:37,212 --> 00:18:38,252
- four, - Go.

417
00:18:38,922 --> 00:18:41,121
- five, six.
- Go.

418
00:18:41,122 --> 00:18:43,151
Hold hands.

419
00:18:43,152 --> 00:18:44,961
Hold hands.

420
00:18:44,962 --> 00:18:47,191
- Slowly.
- Slowly.

421
00:18:47,192 --> 00:18:49,762
- Slowly, go down.
- Go down.

422
00:18:50,662 --> 00:18:53,302
- Jump.
- Jump.

423
00:18:53,732 --> 00:18:55,532
- Like this. One, two, - Jump.

424
00:18:55,802 --> 00:18:57,031
- three, four, - Three.

425
00:18:57,032 --> 00:18:59,272
- This is tiresome.
- five, six, seven,

426
00:18:59,702 --> 00:19:00,742
eight.

427
00:19:03,642 --> 00:19:05,312
Your face is red, Mr. Choi.

428
00:19:06,642 --> 00:19:07,881
(Burning Potato)

429
00:19:07,882 --> 00:19:08,882
- Well done.
- Mr. Choi?

430
00:19:08,883 --> 00:19:11,382
Potato Teacher's face is as red as Eun Soo's clothes.

431
00:19:12,122 --> 00:19:13,881
- You're right.
- A tomato.

432
00:19:13,882 --> 00:19:15,321
You're all warmed up now, right?

433
00:19:15,322 --> 00:19:16,351
- Yes.
- Yes.

434
00:19:16,352 --> 00:19:18,022
- Are you warmed up?
- Yes.

435
00:19:19,092 --> 00:19:21,461
My outfit concept today is Santa Claus.

436
00:19:21,462 --> 00:19:23,431
- Really? You look cute.
- Is that so? Merry Christmas.

437
00:19:23,432 --> 00:19:24,432
