1086
00:50:03,320 --> 00:50:05,920
You're right. They seem to be my kind of person.

1087
00:50:06,020 --> 00:50:07,050
Right?

1088
00:50:08,632 --> 00:50:11,772
(Hyun Wook heads back to the refrigerator.)

1089
00:50:16,542 --> 00:50:17,942
I want to play with the kids.

1090
00:50:19,282 --> 00:50:21,181
I want to go play with them,

1091
