1109
00:51:16,342 --> 00:51:17,572
It's very delicious.

1110
00:51:19,442 --> 00:51:20,772
It's so good.

1111
00:51:20,972 --> 00:51:22,372
- I'm not joking.
- It's so good.

1112
00:51:23,482 --> 00:51:24,542
It's really good.

1113
00:51:29,822 --> 00:51:33,892
