1128
00:52:26,102 --> 00:52:27,712
What?

1129
00:52:28,312 --> 00:52:29,712
What?

1130
00:52:30,442 --> 00:52:32,012
What?

1131
00:52:35,012 --> 00:52:36,552
What?

1132
00:52:37,222 --> 00:52:38,782
What?

1133
00:52:46,762 --> 00:52:48,562
