- Nice to meet you.

1134
00:52:48,892 --> 00:52:50,932
- Hello.
- Hello.

1135
00:52:51,202 --> 00:52:53,372
I missed the timing to come out,

1136
00:52:53,902 --> 00:52:55,232
so I had to stay hidden.

1137
00:52:55,332 --> 00:52:56,901
