1138
00:52:56,902 --> 00:52:58,102
Your buttocks were right here.

1139
00:52:58,742 --> 00:53:00,512
- Really?
- We were cheek to cheek.

1140
00:53:01,172 --> 00:53:03,011
- It was so warm.
- Cheek to cheek?

1141
00:53:03,012 --> 00:53:04,312
(My face was warm thanks to that.)

1142
00:53:04,742 --> 00:53:06,552
- I had no idea.
- I hope we get along.

1143
00:53:06,812 --> 00:53:07,851
Nice to meet you.

1144
00:53:07,852 --> 00:53:08,852
Please eat.

1145
00:53:08,853 --> 00:53:10,021
- It's a celebrity.
- Please eat.

1146
00:53:10,022 --> 00:53:12,521
What are you saying? You're the celebrity.

1147
00:53:12,522 --> 00:53:13,821
- It's a celebrity.
- Celebrity.

1148
00:53:13,822 --> 00:53:16,562
- Hello.
- He's... He's so nice.

1149
00:53:16,762 --> 00:53:19,491
- I saw his drama series, - Did you call him nice?

1150
00:53:19,492 --> 00:53:21,362
