- No. I'm not.

1151
00:53:22,562 --> 00:53:23,901
Right. He was a gangster in many of them.

1152
00:53:23,902 --> 00:53:25,431
Exactly. Please eat.

1153
00:53:25,432 --> 00:53:27,202
I just arrived today.

1154
00:53:27,302 --> 00:53:28,732
- Really?
- From the North Pole.

1155
00:53:29,432 --> 00:53:31,142
