- Did you shoot something there?

1156
00:53:31,502 --> 00:53:32,601
I went to the North Pole for a shoot.

1157
00:53:32,602 --> 00:53:34,542
- I went for a run there.
- Okay.

1158
00:53:35,312 --> 00:53:36,341
