1159
00:53:36,342 --> 00:53:37,941
What is this? Is it a reflection?

1160
00:53:37,942 --> 00:53:39,612
Aurora. This is an aurora.

1161
00:53:40,252 --> 00:53:41,681
- Kian84.
- Really?

1162
00:53:41,682 --> 00:53:43,822
We went to the North Pole together.

1163
00:53:44,982 --> 00:53:47,492
What do we do now? What were you up to all day?

1164
00:53:48,192 --> 00:53:49,192
What is this?

1165
00:53:50,022 --> 00:53:51,621
What do you do all day? Do you stay here?

1166
00:53:51,622 --> 00:53:52,722
I don't know either.

1167
00:53:52,822 --> 00:53:53,992
Do you stay here?

1168
00:53:54,862 --> 00:53:57,362
Today, we went to Gomosanseong Fortress.

1169
00:53:57,802 --> 00:53:58,832
- "Gomo?" - Yes.

1170
00:53:58,932 --> 00:54:00,131
