1187
00:54:41,672 --> 00:54:42,872
It's super sweet.

1188
00:54:43,212 --> 00:54:44,411
Isn't it? Isn't it great?

1189
00:54:44,412 --> 00:54:46,342
- This is great.
- It's amazing.

1190
00:54:46,982 --> 00:54:48,011
It's so sweet.

1191
00:54:48,012 --> 00:54:51,252
