1194
00:54:57,522 --> 00:54:59,962
Yasuo means a strong man.

1195
00:55:01,232 --> 00:55:02,931
That is why I'm Kangnam.

1196
00:55:02,932 --> 00:55:04,401
- I see.
- Yes.

1197
00:55:04,402 --> 00:55:06,161
