1203
00:55:16,212 --> 00:55:17,941
There was a television show set in a school.

1204
00:55:17,942 --> 00:55:20,082
- Yes.
- I was first cast there.

1205
00:55:20,482 --> 00:55:22,981
Then did you meet that friend from the subway...

1206
00:55:22,982 --> 00:55:25,121
- through that show?
- No, that was "I Live Alone."

1207
00:55:25,122 --> 00:55:27,022
- I see, "I Live Alone." - Yes.

1208
00:55:27,792 --> 00:55:30,492
That is why I won't be here in about two days or so.

1209
00:55:31,262 --> 00:55:33,092
- In two days, I have to go...
- Who gave you permission?

1210
00:55:34,832 --> 00:55:37,461
- You just came.
- That subway friend...

1211
00:55:37,462 --> 00:55:38,502
- Yes?
- is getting married.

1212
00:55:39,332 --> 00:55:40,872
- Really?
- He's getting married soon.

1213
00:55:41,202 --> 00:55:42,202
It's his first time.

1214
00:55:42,302 --> 00:55:44,142
I guess I can't say no to that.

1215
00:55:44,342 --> 00:55:48,242
Before you go to the wedding,

1216
00:55:48,872 --> 00:55:50,281
could you make a call?

1217
00:55:50,282 --> 00:55:51,782
- To whom?
- The groom.

1218
00:55:52,612 --> 00:55:53,752
- The groom?
- Yes.

1219
00:55:54,112 --> 00:55:55,652
- The groom?
- And let me talk to him.

1220
00:55:57,122 --> 00:55:58,951
- Why?
- Do you want to get to know him?

1221
00:55:58,952 --> 00:56:00,022
No.

1222
