1224
00:56:05,462 --> 00:56:07,261
- Good idea.
- I'll say something urgent came up.

1225
00:56:07,262 --> 00:56:08,432
Isn't that too much?

1226
00:56:10,702 --> 00:56:12,202
Good idea.

1227
00:56:13,162 --> 00:56:15,671
I'm so happy. It feels like a dream.

1228
00:56:15,672 --> 00:56:16,672
Me too. It's like a dream.

1229
00:56:16,673 --> 00:56:18,402
I was just at the North Pole.

1230
00:56:19,902 --> 00:56:20,911
"Kyung Mo..."

1231
00:56:20,912 --> 00:56:23,072
