1234
00:56:30,022 --> 00:56:31,422
"Lee Ju Eun."

1235
00:56:33,052 --> 00:56:34,222
"Noh Hyo Min."

1236
00:56:35,422 --> 00:56:36,422
"Ha Yun."

1237
00:56:36,423 --> 00:56:37,592
