1238
00:56:38,262 --> 00:56:40,292
"Kim Do Hyun." I think I can remember Kim Do Hyun.

1239
00:56:42,232 --> 00:56:44,732
Anyway, I'll go and try to talk to them tomorrow.

1240
00:56:45,732 --> 00:56:47,631
Tomorrow's class will be just out here.

1241
00:56:47,632 --> 00:56:48,971
- Really?
- Yes.

1242
00:56:48,972 --> 00:56:50,641
- We won't go to the gym.
- Really?

1243
00:56:50,642 --> 00:56:51,871
We normally have classes indoors.

1244
00:56:51,872 --> 00:56:53,711
- Outside?
- Yes, just out here.

1245
00:56:53,712 --> 00:56:55,542
- It's quite warm during the day.
- Yes.

1246
00:56:55,842 --> 00:56:56,842
I see.

