1283
00:58:51,062 --> 00:58:52,292
Cars.

1284
00:58:53,122 --> 00:58:54,832
I like sedans.

1285
00:58:55,632 --> 00:58:57,862
The new Sonata.

1286
00:58:58,162 --> 00:58:59,862
The Benz 4 Series.

1287
